          <div class="about-text">
            <h3>
              Hello! I'm a passionate developer who loves creating digital
              experiences.
            </h3>
            <p>
              With over 5 years of experience in web development, I've worked
              with startups and established companies to build scalable
              applications and beautiful user interfaces. I believe in writing
              clean, maintainable code and creating intuitive user experiences.
            </p>
            <p>
              When I'm not coding, you can find me exploring new technologies,
              contributing to open-source projects, or enjoying a good book with
              a cup of coffee. I'm always eager to learn and take on new
              challenges.
            </p>
            <div class="info-cards">
              <div class="info-card">
                <i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i>
                <div>
                  <span class="info-label">Location</span>
                  <span class="info-value">Coimbatore,Tamil Nadu</span>
                </div>
              </div>
              <div class="info-card">
