              <img
                src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1460925895917-afdab827c52f?w=400&h=250&fit=crop"
                alt="AI-Powered Retinal Disease Diagnosis"
              />
              <div class="project-overlay">
                <div class="project-links">
                  <a href="https://github.com/Silent1715/AI-Powered-Retinal-Disease-Diagnosis-from-OCT-Scans.git" class="project-link">
                    <i class="fas fa-external-link-alt"></i>
                  </a>
                  <a href="https://github.com/Silent1715/AI-Powered-Retinal-Disease-Diagnosis-from-OCT-Scans.git" class="project-link">
                    <i class="fab fa-github"></i>
                  </a>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="project-content">
              <h3>AI-Powered Retinal Disease Diagnosis</h3>
              <p>
                Developed a deep learning model to classify retinal diseases (CNV, DME, DRUSEN, NORMAL) from OCT scan images. 
                Achieved over 95% accuracy using a custom CNN architecture and image preprocessing pipeline.
              </p>
              <div class="project-tech">
                <span class="tech-tag">Python</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">TensorFlow </span>
                <span class="tech-tag">Keras</span>
                <span class="tech-tag">CNN </span>
                <span class="tech-tag">OpenCV</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>



